properties.Name: InterestType
properties.Description:
Interest Type is a larger classification of Interests that enables them to be grouped for presentation or analysis.

For example, the Interest of 'gardening' might be classified by the Interest Type of 'Home Interests' to differentiate those interests from professional or other interests.     

This serves the purpose of grouping interests in larger classifications to give an accurate picture of the consumer in various contexts.

Ex:  
Interest =  "Professional Basketball"
Interest Type = "Sports"

Interest =  "Gardening"
Interest Type = " Home Interests"

Interest =  "Investing"
Interest Type = "Finance"

Each organization will identify, define and track a specific set of AIOs to gather information about, define consumers and make decisions.
